4.00	Pepi,_Luci,_Bom	Pepi, Luci, Bom	Pepi, Luci, Bom y otras chicas del montón (Spanish: ) is a 1980 Spanish film, a campy comedy, written and directed by Pedro Almodóvar. Starring Carmen Maura, Alaska and Eva Siva. The plot follows the wild adventures of three friends: Pepi, an independent modern woman; Luci, a mousy, masochistic housewife; and Bom, a lesbian punk rock singer.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/7/7a/Pepi_Luci_Bom.jpg/220px-Pepi_Luci_Bom.jpg
